# AVPlayer.Status.unknown

**Case**

A value that indicates a player hasn’t attempted to load media for playback.

## Declaration

```swift
case unknown
```

## Discussion

This is the initial state of a player upon creation.

## Status values

- **AVPlayer.Status.readyToPlay**: A value that indicates the player is ready to media.
- **AVPlayer.Status.failed**: A value that indicates the player can no longer play media due to an error.
